<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:0">
      <span class="section-label">Common Questions</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" data-stc="faq_city">Personal Injury Questions in Langley</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" data-faq="faq_cost" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          How much does a personal injury lawyer cost in Langley?
          <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Sidhu Legal works on a contingency fee basis. You pay nothing upfront and we only get paid if we win your case. Your initial consultation is always completely free.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" data-faq="faq_bc_limit" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          How long do I have to file a personal injury claim in BC?
          <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">In British Columbia, the general limitation period is 2 years from the date of the incident. For ICBC claims, you must report within a shorter window. Contact us immediately to protect your rights.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Which court or tribunal handles my Langley claim?<span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span></button>
        <div class="faq-a">It depends on the claim. Many ICBC injury and benefit disputes go through BC's Civil Resolution Tribunal (CRT), while larger lawsuits are filed in the BC Supreme Court, with the New Westminster registry serving the Langley area. We advise you on the right path and handle it for you.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" data-faq="faq_icbc_offer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          What if ICBC already made me an offer?
          <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Do not accept any ICBC settlement without speaking to a lawyer first. Once you accept, you can't reopen your claim. ICBC's first offer is almost always far below what you're entitled to.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" data-faq="faq_fault" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          Can I still claim if the accident was partly my fault?
          <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. BC follows a contributory negligence system. Even if you were partially at fault, you may still recover compensation proportional to the other party's fault. Call us to discuss your specific situation.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" data-faq="faq_bc_serve" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          Do you serve clients outside of Langley?
          <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. We serve clients throughout the Fraser Valley and Lower Mainland including Surrey, Delta, Richmond, Abbotsford, Chilliwack, and beyond. Most meetings can be done by phone or video.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" data-faq="faq_time" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          How long does a personal injury case take?
          <span class="faq-arrow">&#8964;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">It depends on the complexity of your case and the severity of your injuries. Simple cases can settle in a few months. Complex cases can take anywhere from 1 to 3 years. We give you a realistic timeline after reviewing your case.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

